'''Markaz Shabab Al-Am'ari''' ({{lang-ar|مركز شباب الأمعري}}) is a [[State of Palestine|Palestinian]] [[Association football|football]] club, that plays in the [[West Bank Premier League]]. 12,500 capacity [[Faisal Al-Husseini International Stadium]] is their home venue.

==Achievements==

===Domestic===

'''[[West Bank Premier League]]'''
