'''Pine Bowl''' is a 4,000-seat [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Loretto, Pennsylvania]], [[United States]]. It was home to the [[Saint Francis University]] Red Flash [[American football|football]] [[team]].  The facility opened in 1979.
It was replaced by [[DeGol Field]] in 2006.

