'''Stroitel Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Soligorsk]], [[Belarus]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[FC Shakhtyor Soligorsk|Shakhtyor Soligorsk]]. The stadium was built in 1976 and is currently holds 4,200 people.<ref>[http://www.fcshakhter.by/klub/stadion.html Stadium information at Shakhtyor Soligorsk website] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121223044026/http://www.fcshakhter.by/klub/stadion.html |date=2012-12-23 }}</ref>
